---
name: Convert Code to Text
description: A prompt that converts a code snippet into a structural text description.
authors:
  - tjprescott
version: 1.0.0
model:
  api: chat
  configuration:
    type: azure_openai
    api_version: 2025-01-01-preview
    azure_endpoint: ${env:AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT}
    azure_deployment: gpt-4o-mini
  parameters:
    temperature: 0.7
    top_p: 0.95
    stop: []
    frequency_penalty: 0
    presence_penalty: 0
    max_tokens: 16384
sample:
  question: |
    class azure.contoso.NoodleCreateRequest:
      ivar name: str
      ivar color: NoodleColor
  
      def __init__(
        self,
        name: str,
        color: Optional[NoodleColor]
      )
---

system:
You are an AI assistant whose sole job is to convert a given code snippet into a structural description. 

- Identify the language of the code snippet.

- Be concise and technical, free of emojis or embellishments. The output should be a single paragraph. No newlines or bullet points.

- Do not include any code in the output.

- Do not imply or infer the function of any of the code.

user:
{{question}}
